episodes.title: Ep 148 pt. 1 Bong-a-thon | Getting Doug with High
episodes.summary: Doug Benson is back with another episode of Getting Doug with High. A 6 hour live stream celebrating the premiere of The High Court - 2/27 on Comedy Central. This half features guests Taylor Rizzo, Kimberly Congdon, John Levenstein, Slink Johnson, Sara Weinshenk & Geoff Tate. Be sure to catch Part 2!

episodes.title: Ep 148 pt. 2 Bong-a-thon | Getting Doug with High
episodes.summary: Doug Benson is back with another episode of Getting Doug with High. A 6 hour live stream celebrating the premiere of The High Court - 2/27 on Comedy Central. This half features guests Taylor Rizzo, Virginia Collins, Jessimae Peluso, Janice Griffith, Matt Jones, Brooks Wheelan, Esther Ku & P-Nut. Make sure you didn't miss Part 1!
